                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200112-32-victim290 t18200112-32-viclabel175"></join>, and live in Tower-street, Westminster-road. On the 27th of November I sent the prisoner to fetch the articles stated in the indictment, and some money, from my brother's, <placeName id="t18200112-32-crimeloc176">Abbey-street, Bermondsey</placeName>
